A beginners guide to react

Date:
    19 November 2023

Source:
    https://egghead.io/lessons/react-a-beginners-guide-to-react-introduction


Notes:

    Start tool:

        Copy code in 'start' file in terminal

        Allow install

        Open localhost 3,000

    Unpackage

        https://www.unpkg.com/

        Way to run code without using npm install

        
    React uses JSX templating language

        Similar to html

        The browser does not understand it natively

        We use babel for this

    Variables in jsx

        {variable1}{variable2}

    React fragments

        <></> insted of divs

    